rows.label: qst101107_msg0001
rows.name: Welcome, friends, to remote wilderness.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0002
rows.name: You want to make purchase?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh, you sent by Yorgo? He
want the Gulan Walnut?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0004
rows.name: Gulan Walnut cost 10,000G per bit.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0005
rows.name:
Friends want three bits, yes?
That make 30,000G total. Friends
give money and job done.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0006
rows.name:
Friends surprised at pricey price?
Oho, but is no way around!

rows.label: qst101107_msg0007
rows.name:
Gulan Walnut grow with help from
Divine Beast. Friends know this, yes?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0008
rows.name:
And also know that many Divine
Beasts grow weaker lately?
Gula also not unaffected.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0009
rows.name:
So material-grade Gulan Walnut
also in limited supply.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0010
rows.name:
Lumber get rarer, price
get higher. Supply,
demand... Is basically law!

rows.label: qst101107_msg0011
rows.name:
If friends short on currency,
will graciously accept trade
of Muscle Branch.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0012
rows.name:
That also very precious, but admittedly
hard to collect for Nopon...

rows.label: qst101107_msg0040
rows.name:
So, what friends do? Buy with
monies? Or trade for stuff?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0052
rows.name: What shall we do?

rows.label: qst101107_msg0050
rows.name: Pay gold

rows.label: qst101107_msg0051
rows.name: Trade goods

rows.label: qst101107_msg0060
rows.name: See again soon!

rows.label: qst101107_msg0101
rows.name:
Yorgo order three bits of Gulan
Walnut! Me still have enough!

rows.label: qst101107_msg0201
rows.name: Gulan Walnut all sold out.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0202
rows.name:
Maybe not possible to collect
more until such time as
Divine Beast get better.

rows.label: qst101107_msg0203
rows.name:
Business opposite of booming...
Maybe time to up sticks and head
for different Divine Beast.
